OL,3,CFamily 'distraught' as search to find
OL,4,C34-year-old father of one continues
OL,6,FThe family of a man who has been
OL,7,Fmissing since 1 August have said that
OL,8,Fthey are "distraught" and are
OL,9,Fappealing for help to "piece the
OL,10,Fpuzzle together."
OL,12,FMarcus Barter, aged 30, has been
OL,13,Fmissing from the Newport area since
OL,14,Fthe beginning of August.
OL,16,FHis family says he was last seen at
OL,17,Faround 2.30pm on Thursday, 1 August
OL,18,Fnear Coed y Caerau Lane in Newport.
