OL,3,CFamily 'distraught' as search to find
OL,4,C34-year-old father of one continues
OL,6,FThe father-of-one has been described
OL,7,Fby his family as around six foot tall,
OL,8,Fof large build with dark brown hair
OL,9,Fshaved to the back and sides and worn
OL,10,Flonger on top. They say he was last
OL,11,Fseen wearing grey shorts, a grey t-
OL,12,Fshirt and sliders.
OL,14,FMarcus' brother Simon said his
OL,15,Fdisappearance is "completely out of
OL,16,Fcharacter" as he asked the public to
OL,17,Fcheck their CCTV or report any
OL,18,Fsightings. He has stressed how any
OL,19,Finformation, even if considered small,
OL,20,Fis "vital" to the search.
