OL,3,CFamily 'distraught' as search to find
OL,4,C34-year-old father of one continues
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Cymru Wales, Simon
OL,7,Fsaid: "He hasn't come home. All of the
OL,8,Ffamily are distraught. We want to know
OL,9,Fwhere he is. We're not sleeping, we're
OL,10,Fout searching until 3am.
OL,12,F"If you're out there Mark, please let
OL,13,Fus know where you are. Mason, your 4
OL,14,Fyear-old son is asking day in day out
OL,15,Ffor you and we want to know where you
OL,16,Fare."
