OL,3,CFamily 'distraught' as search to find
OL,4,C34-year-old father of one continues
OL,6,FHis mother Nicola added: "Well he's
OL,7,Finevitably going to be struggling with
OL,8,Fhis head because he does on an
OL,9,Feveryday basis anyway, so people need
OL,10,Fto be mindful of that really."
OL,12,FUpon renewing the appeal, Detective
OL,13,FSuperintendent Laura Bartley, who is
OL,14,Fleading the enquiry, said: "We're
OL,15,Fcontinuing to make enquiries in
OL,16,Frelation to our appeal to locate
OL,17,FMarcus.
