OL,3,CFamily 'distraught' as search to find
OL,4,C34-year-old father of one continues
OL,6,F"He was last seen in Coed y Caerau
OL,7,FLane in Newport at around 2.30pm on
OL,8,FThursday 1 August and we're asking
OL,9,Fresidents and businesses to check
OL,10,Ftheir CCTV and appeal to those driving
OL,11,Fin the area to look at their dashcam
OL,12,Ffootage for any later sightings of him.
OL,14,F"If you have any information that you
OL,15,Fthink might help then we want to hear
OL,16,Ffrom you."
